in prison in 2016 after pleading guilty to raping the 12-year-old girl when he was 19.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999996034492473, \"rank\": 3.965508683104419e-07, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His inclusion in the Netherlands team for Paris has sparked outrage, with van de Velde staying in a secret location rather than the athletes' village.\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9874392241766932, \"rank\": 0.012633962661659285, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999725937417, \"rank\": 2.7406176941775734e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999996034492473, \"rank\": 3.965508683104419e-07, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview on LBC, Radcliffe, who will be in Paris working for the BBC, was asked whether there should be rules regarding the participation of certain athletes.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.999999999853344, \"rank\": 1.4654545546949533e-10, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}, {\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9882893352819316, \"rank\": 0.011826819028893508, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999725937417, \"rank\": 2.7406176941775734e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I think that is a very dangerous line to go down given that we allow people who cheat in sport and take drugs in sport to then come back and then compete.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's a tough thing to do to punish him twice and if he's managed to successfully turn his life around after being sent to prison and to qualify and to be playing sport at the highest level, then I actually wish him the best of luck,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four-time Olympian Radcliffe later responded to a post on Twitter/X criticising her remarks as \\\"shocking\\\" by writing: \\\"I agree and can only apologise, that is not what I intended to say.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999807686227, \"rank\": 1.91969929153824e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9882893352819316, \"rank\": 0.011826819028893508, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I stress that it is not something that can be excused in any way.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was\\u2026 responding to the right to ban him from the Games and I do not know why I wished him luck.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Again I apologise.\\\"\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1724, \"end\